{"tid":1963441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔: 理得你無撐警, 無奶共又捐錢, 你年紀大屈唔到你有移民就屌你娶鬼婆","createTime":"2020-04-08T06:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T23:59:19.000Z","uid":34571,"like":31,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"981f99c0ff17c5209719faac77823234c2fbf162","tid":1963441,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"捐25萬助通利琴行被遣散員工 許冠傑4．12網上開騷為港人打氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1962984/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1962984/page/1</a><br />\n依家先知原來咁多人識許冠傑, 係咁話佢移民抵屌, 但又揾唔到證據佢有移民, 講到尾咪又係見人年紀大係名人就要批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 屈完人拍下屎忽就走咗去, 仲有人見屈唔到佢移民就屌佢娶鬼婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n高登時期既時事台噴精咁多年都無變過<br />\n<br />\n黑警藍絲專捉後生仔<br />\n<br />\n連登仔專捉老人, 老就係罪, 係廢老係抵死, 因為連登仔唔會老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692af1e634601f41aeb9937a59cece0af76b7483","tid":1963441,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d41018f85de307c8614e3ce45cad79f19b8641","tid":1963441,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線"},{"pid":"0657bcb88f285c356d55df0e3fcf49ed73ae058e","tid":1963441,"uid":157799,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好怕大家忘記了，可唔可以入嚟幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［5個月］［整合］大家記唔記得今日係咩日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 